    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2017 Shelby GT350, a masterclass in high-revving naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the 5.2L Voodoo V8 featuring a flat-plane crankshaft, pushing power through a precise Tremec TR-3160 six-speed manual gearbox. This example remains mechanically dialed, utilizing MagneRide active damping and a Torsen 3.73 limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Braking performance is anchored by Brembo six-piston front calipers and two-piece cross-drilled rotors. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, and the cooling package remains fully optimized for spirited driving. A purist\u2019s specification with documented service history.",
      "price": 38500.0,
