    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of reliable performance and refined comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, superficial road wear expected of a well-cared-for car. Under the hood, the engine remains responsive and quiet, a testament to a rigorous service history and recent comprehensive fluid checks. Inside, the cabin serves as a clean, smoke-free sanctuary; the upholstery is supple with no significant wear, and every feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates exactly as intended. The tires provide excellent grip with substantial tread life remaining, and the braking is firm and confident. This is a complete, turn-key package for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal.",
      "price": 34500.0,
