    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and maintained over the years. You\u2019ll find it\u2019s super reliable and totally ready to hit the road for its next big adventure right away! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and drives even better, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
